  "title": "Ramp Specialist (Aviation)",
  "description": "<p><strong>​</strong>Our client is a global leader in gateway services, who is seeking to recruit a Ramp Specialist (Aviation). This position is based in Singapore.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Ramp Specialist (Aviation)</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<p>Operate heavy equipment, aerobridges and passenger steps to facilitate flight handling and embarkation / disembarkation of passengers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>· Valid Class 3 driving license (Class 4 driving license would be an advantage)</p>\n<p>· Able to work on rotating shift (6 day work week, rotating shift (can be am, pm or night)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>JJ Consulting Services</p>\n<p>EA Licence No.: 12C6207</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Applicants are invited to send in a MS Word resume to <strong>jobs@jjconsulting.com.sg</strong> stating position applying for/present/expected salaries and earliest available date.<br>\n <br>\nWe thank all applicants in advance and regret that only short listed candidates will be notified.</p>",
